There is no doubt. This whole talk about “freedom” is nothing but a farce. The new government seems to be much worse than the Empire.

But what should I do? There is now way I can overthrow a whole country… No, such things are not within my ability. I could only try to flee from the Republic. But they would stop me. It seems all I can do is to finish this job…

It's frustrating, but the government has me under their control.

